016package org.lifstools.jmzqc;
017
018import java.util.Objects;
019
020/**
021 * Element describing a controlled vocabulary used to refer to the source of the
022 * used CV terms in qualityMetric objects (and others).
023 */
024public class ControlledVocabulary {
025
026    private String name;
027    private String uri;
028    private String version;
029
030    public ControlledVocabulary(){}
031    
032    public ControlledVocabulary(String name, String uri, String version) {
033        this.name = name;
034        this.uri = uri;
035        this.version = version;
036    }
037
038    public String getName() {
039        return name;
040    }
041
042    public void setName(String name) {
043        this.name = name;
044    }
045
046    public String getUri() {
047        return uri;
048    }
049
050    public void setUri(String uri) {
051        this.uri = uri;
052    }
053
054    public String getVersion() {
055        return version;
056    }
057
058    public void setVersion(String version) {
059        this.version = version;
060    }
061
062    @Override
063    public int hashCode() {
064        int hash = 7;
065        hash = 41 * hash + Objects.hashCode(this.name);
066        hash = 41 * hash + Objects.hashCode(this.uri);
067        hash = 41 * hash + Objects.hashCode(this.version);
068        return hash;
069    }
070
071    @Override
072    public boolean equals(Object obj) {
073        if (this == obj) {
074            return true;
075        }
076        if (obj == null) {
077            return false;
078        }
079        if (getClass() != obj.getClass()) {
080            return false;
081        }
082        final ControlledVocabulary other = (ControlledVocabulary) obj;
083        if (!Objects.equals(this.name, other.name)) {
084            return false;
085        }
086        if (!Objects.equals(this.uri, other.uri)) {
087            return false;
088        }
089        return Objects.equals(this.version, other.version);
090    }
091
092}
